text: Suwon Dasan Middle School is a public middle school founded in 2013, located in Suwon, Gyeonggi Province. 1\. History *March 1, 2013 Established *March 1, 2013 The first president, Jeong Eui Ho, was inaugurated. *February 12, 2014 The first graduation ceremony (110 graduates) *March 3, 2014 Entrance ceremony (258 students) *February 10, 2015 The second graduation ceremony (185 graduates) *March 2, 2015 Entrance ceremony (314 students) 2\. The current state *The number of students : 885 (as of March 1, 2015) *The number of school personnel : 62 (as of March 1, 2015) ==References== ==External links== * Category:2013 establishments in South Korea Category:Educational institutions established in 2013 Category:Middle schools in South Korea Category:Schools in Suwon
